Reports unresolved SQL references.
<p>Example (MySQL):</p>
<pre><code>CREATE TABLE users(id INT, name VARCHAR(40));
CREATE TABLE admins(id INT, col1 INT);

SELECT users.id, admins.id FROM admins WHERE admins.id > 1;</code></pre>
<p>The <code>users.id</code> column is unresolved because the <code>users</code> table is missing in the FROM clause.</p>
